column5: Does anyone here fish the Wye River around Saint Marie among the Hurons?  Are there any fish there?  Used to fish here for Crappie when I was a kid (quite a while ago).
You probably can catch pike there now, I,ve also seen all the uglies like carp and dogfish. I'm told there are bass but who knows
lots of carp and gar, very weedy.  lots of panfish and a few pike.
